stylometry: THe decision theory is making the best possible decision for a company or business based on the information you have recieved.  The decision theory assumes that a person will make a decision based off of the information they receive in a model.  FOr instanct if a model states that in order to maximize profit they will need to cut costs or sell a certain amount of products they sell, the decision theory states that the person will make that decision and do what the model suggests in order to receive the results they are hoping to get.  Payoff table is a table that shows us positives and negatives solutions to a problem and places them into tabular form so we are able to see the positives and negatives and are able to make our decision.  They are related because the payoff tables help people make better decisions (based on the decision theory) based on both the positives and negatives where as the decision theory can be associated with only one solution and to either accept or reject the answer or information.
